license-file: LICENSE
author: Federico Mastellone
maintainer: Federico Mastellone
synopsis: AutogenSources
category: PackageTests
build-type: Simple
cabal-version: >= 1.25

description:
    Check that Cabal recognizes the autogen-*-sources fields below.

Library
    autogen-c-sources:  my_autogen_sources.c
    autogen-js-sources: my_autogen_sources.js
    c-sources:          my_sources.c
                        my_autogen_sources.c
    js-sources:         my_sources.js
                        my_autogen_sources.js
    default-language: Haskell2010
    build-depends: base
    exposed-modules:
        MyLibrary
    other-modules:
        MyLibModule

Executable Exe
    autogen-c-sources:  my_autogen_sources.c
    autogen-js-sources: my_autogen_sources.js
    c-sources:          my_sources.c
                        my_autogen_sources.c
    js-sources:         my_sources.js
                        my_autogen_sources.js
    default-language: Haskell2010
    main-is: Dummy.hs
    build-depends: base
    other-modules:
        MyExeModule

Test-Suite Test
    autogen-c-sources:  my_autogen_sources.c
    autogen-js-sources: my_autogen_sources.js
    c-sources:          my_sources.c
                        my_autogen_sources.c
    js-sources:         my_sources.js
                        my_autogen_sources.js
    default-language: Haskell2010
    main-is: Dummy.hs
    type: exitcode-stdio-1.0
    build-depends: base
    other-modules:
        MyTestModule

Benchmark Bench
    autogen-c-sources:  my_autogen_sources.c
    autogen-js-sources: my_autogen_sources.js
    c-sources:          my_sources.c
                        my_autogen_sources.c
    js-sources:         my_sources.js
                        my_autogen_sources.js
    default-language: Haskell2010
    main-is: Dummy.hs
    type: exitcode-stdio-1.0
    build-depends: base
    other-modules:
        MyBenchModule
